      <Content m="2015-11-05T10:04:51.9830713Z">&lt;P&gt;Creating an application is not only about making them functionally effective but also must cover its rendering time. Imagine if the application is so slow that you end up waiting&amp;nbsp;more then few seconds just for it to&amp;nbsp;render.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Spread.Views provides a high performance and simple to use Javascript template engine. Templates offer a way to create HTML chunks that can be automatically merged with JavaScript data.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;Spread.Views provides the support of &lt;STRONG&gt;doT.js&lt;/STRONG&gt; as the template engine for its fastst and concise JavaScript templating function ith emphasis on performance.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;doT.js&lt;/STRONG&gt; is fast, small and has no dependencies. By default, the data in the template must be referenced with &lt;STRONG&gt;'it'&lt;/STRONG&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;
